**`nextGeneration` (refactored):**
- Constants: `0` (length check), `[]` (x2), `1` (hasLiveCells) = 4 x 1 = 4
- Bindings: `grid`, `nextGrid`, `row`, `r`, `cell`, `c`, `hasLiveCells`, `row` (some), `cell` (some) = 9 x 1 = 9
- Invocations: `grid.map`, `row.map`, `getNextCellState`, `nextGrid.some`, `row.some` = 5 x 2 = 10
